quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Boola mbu: ‘‘enyoolele obufimbuli mbu toto omukanda mulala kwa Majini kwarechelesia nikuboola mbu: “efwe toto bwene khuwulile Ikurani yokhuchenyia"
  72,2,"Ilunjisinjia khubulunjifu, mana khuyisuubile, neshikhulisaasia Nyasaye wefu Omulesi nende shiosishiosi tawe"
  72,3,Ne toto bwene Nyasaye wefu niwoluyali olukhongo abula Omukhasi nohomba Omwana
  72,4,Ne khubwatoto abasilu mwifwe baboolanga khu Nyasaye obubeyi
  72,5,Ne efwe toto khwaparanga mbu Abandu nende Amajini shibanyala okhuboola obubeyi khu Nyasaye tawe
  72,6,"Netoto bwene Abasatsa okhurula Mubandu, bakhabanga okhwilinda khubasatsa beshijini, mana nibabameta tsimbi"
  72,7,"Netoto abo baparanga shingala muparanga mbu, Nyasaye shaliruma yesi yesi tawe"
  72,8,Ne toto khwatila khulikulu nikhunyoola lietsulaabalindiabalulunendetsing’ining’ini tsiomulilo
  72,9,Ne toto bwene khwekhalangamwo nikhurechelesia ne uletsa okhurechelesia bulaano alabukanana nende tsing’ining’ini tsiomulilo omululu
  72,10,Ne efwe shikhumanyile tawe nibenyelwa amabii abali khushialo nohomba Nyasaye wabu nabenyela obulunjifu
  72,11,"Ne toto bwene mwifwe khulimwo nende abakholi bamalayi, ne abaandi balimwo balali bario tawe, khuli emikanda chikabukhane"
  72,12,"Ne efwe khwamanya mbu shikhunyala okhushila Nyasaye khushialo tawe, neshikhunyala okhumushila tsimbilo tawe"
  72,13,"Ne efwe olwakhawulila obulunjifu khwabufuchilila. ne usuubila mu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi , sharitsanga okhwibilwa nohomba okhuboolelwa kalali katoto tawe"
  72,14,"Ne toto mwifwe balimwo Abasalamu, nende abalekha katoto, ne balia basilima, abo nibo baloonda obulunjifu"
  72,15,Ne balia balekha obwatoto baliba tsikhwi etsio mulilo kwa jahanam
  72,16,"Ne balunjikhanga khunjila yatoto, khwakhabanywesie amaatsi amaanji"
  72,17,"Khulwo okhubatema khuko, ne ulechelesia amachelo ka Nyasayewe alanyoola eshinyasio eshilulu.’’"
  72,18,"Ne toto emisikiti ni chia Nyasaye , kho mulalaama halala nende Nyasaye shiosishiosi tawe"
  72,19,"Ne toto olwa Omusumba wa Nyasaye yasinjila namulaama, ako (amajini) kalihambi okhumufwinya"
  72,20,"Boola mbu: “ toto esie enamanga Nyasaye wanje omulesi ne shemutsokaasinjiakhwo nende yesi yesi tawe"
  72,21,"Boola mbu: “esie embula obunyali bwokhubawumisia\tnohomba okhubalunjisia"
  72,22,"Boola mbu: “toto abulaho yesiyesi unyala okhuuninda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Nyasaye, ne shindilinyoola andakhelushila tawe halali khuye"
  72,23,"Halali ndusie oburume okhurula khu Nyasaye nende indakano Ye, ne ukhaya Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, kho toto balinyoola Omulilo kwa jahanam, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi"
  72,24,Okhula olwa balilola kabalakungwa balimanya mbu niwina omuteshele mubukhoonyi nende omuleemu
  72,25,"Boolambu:‘ esieengorwakamulakungwa kano nikali ahambi nohomba Nyasaye alakasitia ehale.”"
  72,26,"Omumanyi wakefisile, ne shafunulilanga yesiyesi akefisa tawe"
  72,27,"Halali ulia wayachamila Mubarumwa, ne toto oyo amwelesinjia abalindi imbeli nende inyuma"
  72,28,"Kho anyoole okhumanya toto bosia oburume bwa Nyasaye wabu, naye yamanya obulayi akabali ninako, ne yamanya obubasio bwabuli eshindu"